About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. тАЬAlphaтАЭ, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: O Pata Nahi Ji Konsa Nasha Krta Hai Full Video Song | Yaar Mera Tittliyan Varga Song | Hardy Sandhu
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies Presents an interesting take on a heart break story featuring Harrdy Sandhu and Sargun Mehta. The song is sung by the super melodious Afsana Khan and its music has been done by Super talented and our own artist Avvy Sra. The deep meaning of the lyrics are written by none other than JAANI and this new conceptual video has been directed by ace video director Arvindr Khaira.

Singer :- Afsana Khan
Music :- Avvy Sra

DOP :- Anurag Solanki

Yash Kumarr Entertainment brings you the soul-stirring Krishna bhajan "Mori Maiya Re" тАФ sung by the talented Yash Kumarr, composed by Narendra Sagar, and penned by Rajesh Mishra.

This heart-touching video song beautifully portrays the divine bond between Lord Krishna and his mother Yashoda Maiya. A must-watch this Janmashtami or whenever your heart craves devotion.

snippet.title: Lanmi - Official Music Video Release | 13th August | Patriots' Day | Kenedy Khuman
snippet.description:
On this 13th August (PatriotsтАЩ Day), we salute the brave martyrs who laid down their lives for our motherland.
We also salute the countless everyday heroes who continue to serve and protect our land in their own ways. From farmers who feed us, teachers who shape our minds, artisans who preserve our culture, doctors who heal, to workers who build and safeguard our communities each is a soldier in their own right, standing guard for the future of Manipur.
This song is a heartfelt tribute to every profession, every hard-working soul, and every unsung hero whose dedication keeps the spirit of our motherland alive.

13th August PatriotsтАЩ Day na Lakpasida Ema Leibak Nungshibagi, Ema leibakpu ngakcha senjabagi firep amuk henna chetsinhanlasi. Eikhoi esana ngamjaba magi magi thoudang louduna punna hotnaminnasi . Emagidamak eikhoi khudingmak тАЬLanmiтАЭ ni.
